# aria2c - Vendored Binary

**Version**: 1.37.0 (win-64bit)
**License**: GNU General Public License v2.0 (GPL-2.0)
**Source**: <https://github.com/aria2/aria2>
**Release**: <https://github.com/aria2/aria2/releases/tag/release-1.37.0>

aria2 is a lightweight multi-protocol & multi-source command-line download
utility. It is used by UmeAiRT-Toolkit for accelerated model downloads with
multi-connection support.
